{"tid":1633352,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"三毛打手已進化兩邊吹風 代表人地開始急","createTime":"2019-10-07T03:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:00:09.000Z","uid":189404,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"99b4375f16d2dd64718d7c9e05f699641545b8e3","tid":1633352,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:36:58.000Z","msg":"呢幾日風向唔同之前推向一邊，係兩邊吹將和理非勇武兩邊極端化。細究底下佢地既回覆大多只係情緒化。目的係分化我地。<br />\n<br />\n代表咩？！人地開始急，開始急咁點，我地就拖住黎做，唔係唔做，彈入彈出你咬我食呀。節奏慢落黎，和勇文宣方可同步節奏消化。<br />\n<br />\n講到呢到跟住又會有三毛屌鳩我唔夠勇。大佬拖住做集中做唔代表唔勇，可以代表陰陰濕濕你估我唔到。可以集中力量，水滴石穿，又唔引起反彈。<br />\n<br />\n和就又唔洗一定要和哂，大氛圍係和就得。其他小氛圍既勇自然可以理解。<br />\n<br />\n呢個狀態既和有個好處係一定唔會錯。<br />\n<br />\n當然你可以咬我吹風，我吹中間偏和風。"},{"pid":"f256676e7883366c2aa9fb9176af1657fd4814eb","tid":1633352,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2edd0ba2bedbde6fdbad583ff1f673fb000ce52d","tid":1633352,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43dff2aa463fb456d3142b19ce8286c5f449509b","tid":1633352,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ac45e1e9c527102f576cc0a16e55a3635cf759","tid":1633352,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:39:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd2dfb92963c6e8fccc2a330718b91499994e6de","tid":1633352,"uid":30582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:40:38.000Z","msg":"老老實實，這是我見過現在最好的做法。"},{"pid":"9f3bd2479482fe357b14b0c777442f11c01429fc","tid":1633352,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:43:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"784659662cbc64265c291b7bc7fc1704bdbafc30","tid":1633352,"uid":1